<plot>A sailor on leave (Jay Norris) falls in love with the voice of a juke-box ("soundies"-type box) girl but his friend, not wanting him to get involved, ruins the machine. The Girl (Gail Davis) gets Stan Kenton and his orchestra to present five musical selections, with June Christy and The Pastels on the vocals. True love wins out.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?333537</url></doc>
